#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When two or more people are working on a file and passing it back and forth "
"between one another, it becomes difficult to see what changes have been made "
"to a new version or copy of the file. Opening the new copy and the original, "
"side-by-side in the application used to create it is one solution but, "
"laborious, time consuming, and prone to error. This is where a program to "
"show differences, diffs for short, is useful."
msgstr ""
"Ko dve ali več oseb dela na datoteki in si jo med seboj izmenjujejo, je "
"težko ugotoviti, katere spremembe so bile vnesene v novo različico ali "
"kopijo datoteke. Odpiranje nove kopije in izvirnika drug ob drugem v "
"aplikaciji, s katero sta bila ustvarjena, je ena od rešitev, vendar je "
"zamudna, dolgotrajna in nagnjena k napakam. Tu je uporaben program za "
"prikazovanje razlik, skrajšano diffs."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As would be expected, an appropriate name for such a program would be "
"<quote>diff</quote>. As it happens, the program <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu."
"org/software/diffutils/\">diff</ulink> is installed on most &Linux;-based "
"systems and is used for exactly this purpose. Developers often use diff, as "
"a command line tool, to show differences between versions of a source code "
"file. However, the use of diff is not limited to showing differences in code "
"source files, it can be used on many text-based file types."
msgstr ""
"Po pričakovanjih bi bilo primerno ime za tak program <quote>diff</quote>. "
"Program <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/diffutils/\">diff</ulink> "
"je nameščen v večini sistemov, ki temeljijo na operacijskem sistemu &Linux; "
"in se uporablja prav v ta namen. Razvijalci pogosto uporabljajo orodje za "
"ukazno vrstico diff za prikaz razlik med različicami datotek izvorne kode. "
"Vendar pa uporaba razlikovanja ni omejena na prikazovanje razlik v izvornih "
"datotekah s kodo, temveč se lahko uporablja za številne vrste besedilnih "
"datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using diff from the command line can be confusing, learning the diff command "
"syntax and deciphering the output can bewilder most people. This is where "
"&kompare; comes into play. Providing a graphical front-end to the diff "
"program, the interface displays source and destination files side-by-side "
"with all differences automatically highlighted. From this starting point, "
"changes in one file can be sequentially applied to the other file on a "
"selective and controlled basis. Not all changes need to be applied and if "
"you do apply a change it can always be &apos;unapplied&apos;. When all "
"required changes have been applied they can be saved and will display as "
"normal in the original application used to create the file."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba ukazov za razlikovanje iz ukazne vrstice je lahko zmedena, učenje "
"sintakse ukazov za razlikovanje in dešifriranje izpisa lahko večino ljudi "
"zmede. Tu pride v poštev funkcija &kompare;. Vmesnik, ki je grafični vmesnik "
"programa za razlikovanje, prikazuje izvorne in ciljne datoteke drugo ob "
"drugi, pri čemer so vse razlike samodejno označene. S tega izhodišča se "
"lahko spremembe v eni datoteki zaporedno zaporedoma uporabijo v drugi "
"datoteki na selektivni in nadzorovani podlagi. Vseh sprememb ni treba "
"uporabiti, in če spremembo uporabite, jo lahko vedno &apos;"
"neuporabljen&apos;. Ko so bile uporabljene vse zahtevane spremembe, jih "
"lahko shranite in bodo prikazane kot običajno v prvotni aplikaciji, ki je "
"bila uporabljena za ustvarjanje datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to displaying differences between a source and destination file, "
"&kompare; can be used to create and view a special file called a &apos;"
"diff&apos;. This file captures the differences between the two sources into "
"a single file that can be used to view and apply changes to any other copy "
"of the file. For example, if two people are editing a document. The first "
"person wants to make changes and send just the changes made to the second "
"person. Normally, the first person would send a complete copy of the "
"modified document to the second person, who would then have to compare the "
"modified document side-by-side with unmodified version. The process for this "
"is much like what we have described in the previous paragraphs. With "
"&kompare; the first person would first make a local copy of the file to be "
"modified, then make changes and compare the original and modified copy. Now "
"using &kompare; a diff file can be created that captures only the changes "
"made. This can be sent to the second person in place of a whole file "
"containing the changes."
msgstr ""
"Poleg prikaza razlik med izvorno in ciljno datoteko lahko s programom "
"&kompare; ustvarite in prikažete posebno datoteko, imenovano &apos;"
"diff&apos;. V tej datoteki so razlike med obema viroma zajete v eni sami "
"datoteki, ki jo je mogoče uporabiti za pregledovanje in uporabo sprememb v "
"kateri koli drugi kopiji datoteke. Če na primer dokument urejata dve osebi. "
"Prva oseba želi opraviti spremembe in drugi osebi poslati samo opravljene "
"spremembe. Običajno bi prva oseba poslala celotno kopijo spremenjenega "
"dokumenta drugi osebi, ki bi nato morala primerjati spremenjeni dokument z "
"nespremenjeno različico. Postopek je podoben tistemu, ki smo ga opisali v "
"prejšnjih odstavkih. S funkcijo &kompare; bi prva oseba najprej naredila "
"lokalno kopijo datoteke, ki jo je treba spremeniti, nato bi opravila "
"spremembe in primerjala izvirno in spremenjeno kopijo. Zdaj lahko z uporabo "
"funkcije &kompare; ustvarite datoteko z razlikami, v kateri so zajete samo "
"opravljene spremembe. To lahko pošljete drugi osebi namesto celotne datoteke "
"s spremembami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using &kompare; the second person can view the diff file, compare it to the "
"local copy of the document and apply the changes made by the first person. "
"So the process can go on for many versions of the document, each person "
"making changes, creating diffs, distributing them and applying them. This "
"process is commonly called <quote>patching</quote> , a term taken from the "
"program named <quote>patch</quote> which is another command line tool "
"specifically designed for the purpose of applying diff files."
msgstr ""
"Druga oseba si lahko z uporabo funkcije &kompare; ogleda datoteko razlike, "
"jo primerja z lokalno kopijo dokumenta in uporabi spremembe, ki jih je "
"opravila prva oseba. Tako se lahko postopek nadaljuje za več različic "
"dokumenta, pri čemer vsaka oseba vnaša spremembe, ustvarja razlike, jih "
"razpošilja in uporablja. Ta postopek se običajno imenuje <quote>krpanje</"
"quote> , izraz pa je prevzet iz programa <quote>patch</quote>, ki je še eno "
"orodje ukazne vrstice, posebej zasnovano za uporabo datotek z razlikami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It sometimes happens that people edit a file at the same time. In this "
"situation it is likely that people will make changes in the document at "
"exactly the same line. This creates a problem because, without applied "
"caution, people could be overwriting each others work as they apply the diff "
"files they receive. Fortunately the developers of the diff and patch "
"programs took this into consideration and so these tools will not allow such "
"changes to be applied without manual intervention. When this state is "
"reached, it is known as a <quote>conflict</quote> . &kompare; will display "
"conflicts so that you can manually resolve them, deciding which changes "
"should be applied to which file."
msgstr ""
"Včasih se zgodi, da ljudje hkrati urejajo datoteko. V tem primeru je "
"verjetno, da bodo ljudje vnesli spremembe v dokument v natanko isti vrstici. "
"To predstavlja težavo, saj bi lahko ljudje brez previdnosti pri uporabi "
"prejetih datotek z razlikami prepisovali delo drug drugega. Na srečo so "
"razvijalci programov za razlikovanje in popravke to upoštevali, zato ta "
"orodja ne bodo omogočala uporabe takšnih sprememb brez ročnega posredovanja. "
"Ko je to stanje doseženo, se imenuje <quote>konflikt</quote> . &kompare; "
"prikaže konflikte, tako da jih lahko ročno rešite in se odločite, katere "
"spremembe naj se uporabijo za katero datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kompare; is also a great program for comparison of file changes on a folder "
"level. When used to compare folders &kompare; recursively examines "
"subfolders and their file contents for differences. In this use case, each "
"file where differences are found are automatically opened and listed by "
"&kompare; where easy navigation between the various files is possible."
msgstr ""
"&kompare; je tudi odličen program za primerjavo sprememb datotek na ravni "
"mape. Pri uporabi za primerjavo map &kompare; rekurzivno preveri podmape in "
"njihovo vsebino datotek za iskanje razlik. V tem primeru uporabe se vsaka "
"datoteka, v kateri so ugotovljene razlike, samodejno odpre in izpiše s "
"programom &kompare; pri tem je mogoča enostavna navigacija med različnimi "
"datotekami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kompare;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kompare;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "Kako začeti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section provides instructions for starting &kompare; and provides a "
"quick tour to the &kompare; main interface."
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku so navodila za zagon programa &kompare; in hiter ogled "
"glavnega vmesnika programa &kompare;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting &kompare;"
msgstr "Začetek &kompare;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A shortcut for starting &kompare; can be found in the application menu in "
"the Development group <menuchoice><guimenu>Development</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Kompare</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Bližnjico za zagon programa &kompare; najdete v meniju aplikacije v skupini "
"Razvoj <menuchoice><guimenu>Razvoj</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kompare</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When &kompare; starts the first thing it does is display a dialog from which "
"to select the files you wish to compare. Special settings for the properties "
"of the diff and the appearance thereof can also be selected. In the file "
"form select a source and destination source to compare. This can be any two "
"files, folders or a &URL; and a file. Once the source and destination are "
"selected click the <guibutton>Compare</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ko se program &kompare; zažene, najprej prikaže pogovorno okno, v katerem "
"izberete datoteke, ki jih želite primerjati. Izberete lahko tudi posebne "
"nastavitve za lastnosti razlike in njen videz. V obrazcu za datoteke "
"izberite izvorni in ciljni vir za primerjavo. To sta lahko dve poljubni "
"datoteki, mapi ali &URL; in datoteka. Ko sta izbrana izvor in cilj, kliknite "
"gumb <guibutton>Primerjaj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once &kompare; has discovered the differences it will display the main "
"interface. When comparing two files or a URL and a file the process takes "
"just a few seconds. However, when comparing folders with many subfolders and "
"files, this process can take awhile."
msgstr ""
"Ko &kompare; odkrije razlike, prikaže glavni vmesnik. Primerjava dveh "
"datotek ali URL in datoteke traja le nekaj sekund. Če primerjate mape s "
"številnimi podmapami in datotekami, lahko ta postopek traja nekaj časa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For explanation of the options available from diff and appearance forms see "
"<xref linkend=\"configure-preferences\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Za razlago možnosti, ki so na voljo v obrazcih za razlikovanje in videz, "
"glejte <xref linkend=\"configure-preferences\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main Interface"
msgstr "Glavni vmesnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section provides a quick tour of the main interface which is comprised "
"of the following areas:"
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku je na voljo hiter ogled glavnega vmesnika, ki ga sestavljajo "
"naslednja področja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Menus</para>"
msgstr "<para>Meni</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Toolbar</para>"
msgstr "<para>Orodna vrstica</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Source and Destination Folders</para>"
msgstr "<para>Izvorne in ciljne mape</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Source and Destination Files</para>"
msgstr "<para>Izvorne in ciljne datoteke</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Source and Destination Line Changes</para>"
msgstr "<para>Izvorne in ciljne spremembe vrstice</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Source and Destination Text View"
msgstr "Prikaz izvornega in ciljnega besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Statusbar</para>"
msgstr "<para>Statusna vrstica</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Menus</title>"
msgstr "<title>Meni</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kompare; provides a menu driven interface. Explanation to the menu items "
"and their options is provided in <xref linkend=\"command-reference\"/>."
msgstr ""
"&kompare; zagotavlja vmesnik, ki ga poganja meni. Pojasnila k elementom "
"menija in njihovim možnostim so na voljo v <xref linkend=\"command-reference"
"\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Toolbar</title>"
msgstr "<title>Orodna vrstica</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kompare; toolbar provides shortcuts to the most frequently used diff "
"and merge operations. The toolbar orientation, text positioning, icon size "
"properties and which shortcut icons are displayed can be customized from the "
"toolbar context menu accessed when right-clicking the toolbar with the "
"mouse. The toolbar context menu also enables the toolbar to be hidden. If "
"the toolbar is hidden and you wish to unhide it, select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Toolbar</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Orodna vrstica &kompare; omogoča bližnjice za najpogosteje uporabljene "
"operacije razlikovanja in združevanja. Orientacijo orodne vrstice, "
"postavitev besedila, lastnosti velikosti ikon in prikazane ikone bližnjic "
"lahko prilagodite v kontekstnem meniju orodne vrstice, do katerega dostopate "
"z desnim klikom miške na orodno vrstico. Kontekstni meni orodne vrstice "
"omogoča tudi skrivanje orodne vrstice. Če je orodna vrstica skrita in jo "
"želite odkriti, izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži orodno vrstico</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Source and Destination Folders</title>"
msgstr "<title>Izvorne in ciljne mape</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The source folder and destination folder panes display the folders in which "
"compared files reside. When many subfolders are included in the comparison, "
"then selecting a folder will display the first document in that folder where "
"a difference was found between the source and destination."
msgstr ""
"V podoknu izvorne in ciljne mape so prikazane mape, v katerih se nahajajo "
"primerjane datoteke. Če je v primerjavo vključenih veliko podmap, se ob "
"izbiri mape prikaže prvi dokument v tej mapi, pri katerem je bila "
"ugotovljena razlika med izvornim in ciljnim dokumentom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Source and Destination Files</title>"
msgstr "<title>Izvorne in ciljne datoteke</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The source and destination file pane displays files where a difference was "
"found for the currently selected source or destination folder. When a folder "
"has multiple documents containing differences, all documents with a "
"difference are listed. The selected document is displayed."
msgstr ""
"V podoknu izvorne in ciljne datoteke so prikazane datoteke, pri katerih je "
"bila za trenutno izbrano izvorno ali ciljno mapo ugotovljena razlika. Če je "
"v mapi več dokumentov z razlikami, so navedeni vsi dokumenti z razlikami. "
"Prikaže se izbrani dokument."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Source and Destination Line Changes</title>"
msgstr "<title>Izvorne in ciljne spremembe vrstice</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The source and destination line changes pane summarizes the differences "
"found between the current source and destination documents. Selecting a "
"record within the pane highlights and selects the difference. This is a "
"useful way to navigate and inspect long documents with many differences."
msgstr ""
"V podoknu Spremembe izvorne in ciljne vrstice so povzete razlike, "
"ugotovljene med trenutnimi izvornimi in ciljnimi dokumenti. Z izbiro zapisa "
"v podoknu se poudari in izbere razlika. To je uporaben način za navigacijo "
"in pregledovanje dolgih dokumentov z veliko razlikami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Source and Destination View"
msgstr "Pogled vira in cilja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The source and destination view is the main workspace of &kompare;. The "
"contents and highlighted differences of the currently selected source and "
"destination file are displayed here with line numbers."
msgstr ""
"Pogled vira in cilja je glavni delovni prostor programa &kompare;. Tu so "
"prikazani vsebina in označene razlike trenutno izbrane izvorne in ciljne "
"datoteke s številkami vrstic."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text View"
msgstr "Prikaz besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Text View</guilabel> is not displayed by default. It can be "
"opened by selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show "
"Text View</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Prikaz Besedila</guilabel> privzeto ni prikazan. Odprete ga lahko "
"z izbiro <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži "
"besedilni prikaz</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Statusbar</title>"
msgstr "<title>Statusna vrstica</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The status bar provides a summary of the current source and destination file "
"or folder under comparison. The status bar also reports the number of "
"changes found in the current document and counts the differences that have "
"been applied. Furthermore, the status bar shows the overall number of "
"documents containing differences and the current document number selected "
"from this set. For example, a comparison run over two folders may return "
"1890 files with differences. The currently selected document is number 18 of "
"1890."
msgstr ""
"V vrstici stanja je prikazan povzetek trenutne izvorne in ciljne datoteke "
"ali mape, ki ju primerjate. Vrstica stanja poroča tudi o številu najdenih "
"sprememb v trenutnem dokumentu in šteje razlike, ki so bile uporabljene. "
"Poleg tega je v vrstici stanja prikazano skupno število dokumentov, ki "
"vsebujejo razlike, in trenutna številka dokumenta, izbranega iz tega niza. "
"Primerjava dveh map lahko na primer vrne 1890 datotek z razlikami. Trenutno "
"izbrani dokument je številka 18 od 1890."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Viewing Differences"
msgstr "Pregledovanje razlik"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing Screen Real-Estate"
msgstr "Upravljanje zaslona nepremičnin"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kompare; displays the source and destination file under using equal "
"percentage of the main interface view work area. This view area provides "
"some features that help optimize use of screen real-estate while viewing "
"differences, including:"
msgstr ""
"&kompare; prikaže izvorno in ciljno datoteko v enakem odstotku delovnega "
"območja glavnega vmesnika. To območje prikaza ponuja nekaj funkcij, ki "
"pomagajo optimizirati uporabo zaslonskega prostora med pregledovanjem "
"razlik, med drugim:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dual Scrollbars"
msgstr "Dvojne drsne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The most obvious feature is that scrollbars are provided both on the right "
"and bottom edges of the view area. Using the scrollbars it is possible to "
"move rapidly through the comparison."
msgstr ""
"Najbolj očitna lastnost je, da so na desnem in spodnjem robu prikaznega "
"območja na voljo vrstice za pomikanje. Z uporabo drsnih črt se lahko hitro "
"premikate po primerjavi."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Share Grip Handle"
msgstr "Skupna uporaba ročaja za oprijem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The vertical space between the source and destination view not only makes it "
"possible to clearly see the start and end of lines in each of the panes, but "
"is also a grip handle that allows adjustment of percentage occupied between "
"the source and destination views that comprise the view pane. To change pane "
"size for one of the views, hover the mouse pointer over the grip handle then "
"hold down the mouse button and drag left or right. Naturally, increasing the "
"area of one pane will decrease the area available to the opposite pane "
"within the view panel area."
msgstr ""
"Navpični prostor med izvornim in ciljnim prikazom ne omogoča le jasnega "
"pogleda na začetek in konec vrstic v vsaki plošči, temveč je tudi ročica, ki "
"omogoča nastavitev odstotka zasedenosti med izvornim in ciljnim prikazom, ki "
"sestavljata ploščo pogleda. Če želite spremeniti velikost plošče enega od "
"pogledov, se z miškinim kazalcem pomaknite nad ročaj za oprijem, nato "
"pridržite pritisnjen gumb miške in povlecite v levo ali desno. Seveda, če "
"povečate površino ene plošče, se zmanjša površina, ki je na voljo drugi "
"plošči v območju pogleda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A second horizontal handle is available between the navigation panel and the "
"source and destination view."
msgstr ""
"Drugi vodoravni ročaj je na voljo med navigacijsko ploščo ter izvornim in "
"ciljnim prikazom."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid "Docking"
msgstr "Priključitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The navigation panel can be undocked from the main interface by clicking the "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"undock.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icon located top right of the "
"panel. This opens it in a window of its own, allowing you to move it across "
"the screen. You can even hide the navigation panel by clicking the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"dock.png\" format=\"PNG"
"\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icon. To display a hidden navigation "
"bar again, click with the &RMB; into the menubar and select "
"<guilabel>Navigation</guilabel> from the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Navigacijsko ploščo lahko z glavnega vmesnika odvežete tako, da kliknete "
"ikono <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"undock.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>, ki se nahaja zgoraj "
"desno od plošče. Tako ga odprete v lastnem oknu in ga lahko premikate po "
"zaslonu. Navigacijsko ploščo lahko skrijete tudi tako, da kliknete ikono "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"dock.png\" format=\"PNG"
"\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>. Če želite ponovno prikazati skrito "
"navigacijsko vrstico, kliknite z &RMB; v menijska vrstica in v kontekstnem "
"meniju izberite <guilabel>Navigacija</guilabel>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Statusbar Toggle"
msgstr "Preklapljanje statusne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The status bar of the view panel can be toggled on and off by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Statusbar</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Vrstico stanja na prikazni plošči lahko vklopite in izklopite z izbiro "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži vrstico stanja</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switching Source and Destination Views"
msgstr "Preklapljanje pogledov vira in cilja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sometimes it can be useful to consider what the file to which differences "
"where to be applied as the source. For example, when comparing two modified "
"versions of a file and discovering that one file has many more modifications "
"than the other. The file with more changes would be better as the source, "
"since then fewer differences would need to be applied."
msgstr ""
"Včasih je lahko koristno upoštevati, katera datoteka, v kateri se "
"uporabljajo razlike, je vir. Na primer, ko primerjate dve spremenjeni "
"različici datoteke in ugotovite, da ima ena datoteka veliko več sprememb kot "
"druga. Datoteka z več spremembami bi bila boljša kot vir, saj bi bilo treba "
"uveljaviti manj razlik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this case select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Swap "
"Source with Destination</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This will switch the "
"files displayed in all &kompare; panels."
msgstr ""
"V tem primeru izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Zamenjava vira z namembnim krajem</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. S tem boste preklopili datoteke, prikazane na vseh ploščah "
"&kompare;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displaying Difference Statistics"
msgstr "Prikaz statistike razlik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a quick overview of the differences, select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Statistics</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. This will "
"display the <guilabel>Diff Statistics</guilabel> dialog. The following "
"information is provided:"
msgstr ""
"Za hiter pregled razlik izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži statistiko</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Prikaže "
"se pogovorno okno <guilabel>Statistika razlik</guilabel>. Na voljo so "
"naslednje informacije:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Old file:"
msgstr "Stara datoteka:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The file name of what is usually the source file or file that is unmodified."
msgstr ""
"Ime datoteke, ki je običajno izvorna datoteka ali datoteka, ki ni "
"spremenjena."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "New file:"
msgstr "Nova datoteka:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The file name of what is usually the destination file or file that is "
"modified and to which differences will be applied."
msgstr ""
"Ime datoteke, ki je običajno ciljna datoteka ali datoteka, ki se spremeni in "
"za katero se uporabijo razlike."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "Format:"
msgstr "Format:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The diff format used to display the difference (see <xref linkend=\"diff-"
"format\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Oblika razlike, ki se uporablja za prikaz razlike (glejte <xref linkend="
"\"diff-format\"/>)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of hunks:"
msgstr "Število kosov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "The number of hunks found in the difference."
msgstr "Število kosov v razliki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A hunk is a <quote>c<emphasis>hunk</emphasis></quote> of lines that have "
"been marked as different between source and destination and may include "
"context lines depending on the diff format <guilabel>Lines of Context</"
"guilabel> value (see <xref linkend=\"diff-format\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Kos je <quote>c<emphasis>del</emphasis></quote> vrstic, ki so bile označene "
"kot različne med izvorom in ciljem in lahko vključujejo vrstice konteksta, "
"odvisno od vrednosti <guilabel>Vrstice konteksta</guilabel> formata razlike "
"(glejte <xref linkend=\"diff-format\"/>)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of differences"
msgstr "Število razlik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The actual number of differences found, not hunks. A hunk can contain one or "
"more differences when the line change range and the context lines of any two "
"or more changes overlap."
msgstr ""
"Dejansko število najdenih razlik, ne kosov. V kosu je lahko ena ali več "
"razlik, če se območje sprememb vrstic in kontekstne vrstice katerih koli "
"dveh ali več sprememb prekrivajo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigating the Difference View"
msgstr "Navigacija v prikazu razlik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kompare; enables rapid navigation of differences on a file level and of "
"multiple difference files when comparing folder trees."
msgstr ""
"&kompare; omogoča hitro iskanje razlik na ravni datotek in več datotek z "
"razlikami pri primerjavi dreves map."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting a Difference"
msgstr "Izbira razlike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "A difference can be selected using by:"
msgstr "Razliko lahko izberete z:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"clicking a line in the Source and Destination Line Changes pane (top right "
"of the main window)."
msgstr ""
"s klikom na vrstico v podoknu Spremembe izvorne in ciljne vrstice (zgoraj "
"desno v glavnem oknu)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "clicking the highlighted difference in the View pane."
msgstr "klikom na označeno razliko v podoknu Pogled."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"traversing the listed differences in a comparison (see <xref linkend="
"\"traversing-differences\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"premagovanje naštetih razlik v primerjavi (glejte <xref linkend=\"traversing-"
"differences\"/>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a difference is selected it is considered to be <quote>in focus</quote> "
"and is displayed in a brighter color that non-selected differences."
msgstr ""
"Ko je razlika izbrana, se šteje, da je <quote>v fokusu</quote>, in je "
"prikazana v svetlejši barvi kot neizbrane razlike."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Traversing Differences"
msgstr "Premagovanje razlik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a comparison finds many differences one of the best ways to approach "
"reviewing them is to traverse the differences in a logical order, usually "
"from top to bottom."
msgstr ""
"Kadar je pri primerjavi ugotovljenih veliko razlik, je eden od najboljših "
"načinov za pregledovanje teh razlik, da jih pregledamo v logičnem vrstnem "
"redu, običajno od zgoraj navzdol."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default &kompare; selects the first difference found in a comparison. By "
"selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Difference</guimenu><guimenuitem>Next "
"Difference</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>Down</keycap></keycombo>) the difference following the current "
"selection is brought into focus. To select the difference before the current "
"difference select <menuchoice><guimenu>Difference</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Previous Difference</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Up</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto &kompare; izbere prvo razliko, najdeno v primerjavi. Z izbiro "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Razlika</guimenu><guimenuitem>Naslednja razlika</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Down</"
"keycap></keycombo>) se izostri razlika, ki sledi trenutnemu izboru. Če "
"želite izbrati razliko pred trenutno razliko, izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Razlika</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prejšnja razlika</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Up</"
"keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this way it is possible to traverse differences in an orderly manner, "
"applying and unapply differences upon review."
msgstr ""
"Na ta način je mogoče razlike odpraviti na urejen način, pri čemer se "
"razlike ob pregledu uporabijo in ne uporabijo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switching Between Files"
msgstr "Preklapljanje med datotekami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a comparison is performed on folder level, many files may be found with "
"differences. A complete list of the files compared with difference found is "
"provided in the <quote>Source and Destination Folders</quote>, and "
"<quote>Source and Destination Files</quote> panes. However, &kompare; "
"displays differences between source and destination one comparison at time."
msgstr ""
"Pri primerjavi na ravni mape se lahko najdejo razlike med številnimi "
"datotekami. Celoten seznam primerjanih datotek z najdenimi razlikami je na "
"voljo v podoknih <quote>Izvorne in ciljne mape</quote> ter <quote>Izvorne in "
"ciljne datoteke</quote>. S funkcijo &kompare; pa se razlike med izvorom in "
"ciljem prikažejo po ena primerjava naenkrat."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To switch between documents in this scenario the following options are "
"available:"
msgstr ""
"Za preklapljanje med dokumenti v tem scenariju so na voljo naslednje "
"možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the <quote>Source and Destination Folders</quote> pane to display "
"file differences found in the <quote>Source and Destination Files</quote> "
"pane, then select a file."
msgstr ""
"Izberite podokno <quote>Izvorne in ciljne mape</quote>, da prikažete razlike "
"med datotekami, najdenimi v podoknu <quote>Izvorne in ciljne datoteke</"
"quote>, nato pa izberite datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <menuchoice><guimenu>Difference</guimenu><guimenuitem>Previous File</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>PgUp</"
"keycap></keycombo>) or <menuchoice><guimenu>Difference</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Next File</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>PgDown</keycap></keycombo>) to display the previous "
"or next difference file found in the <quote>Source and Destination Files</"
"quote> pane."
msgstr ""
"Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Razlika</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prejšnja "
"datoteka</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>PgUp</keycap></keycombo>) ali <menuchoice><guimenu>Razlika</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Naslednja datoteka</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>PgDown</keycap></keycombo>), da "
"prikažete prejšnjo ali naslednjo datoteko razlike, najdeno v podoknu "
"<quote>Izhodne in ciljne datoteke</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "Merging Differences"
msgstr "Združevanje razlik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kompare; makes the task of applying and unapplying differences as simple as "
"point and click. Multiple apply and unapply operations can be performed on a "
"difference as all operations are performed in memory and not written to the "
"files on disk until the save operation is performed."
msgstr ""
"&kompare; omogoča, da je uporaba in odprava razlik tako preprosta, kot da "
"pokažete in kliknete. Na razliki lahko izvedete več operacij uporabe in "
"neuporabe, saj se vse operacije izvedejo v pomnilniku in se ne zapišejo v "
"datoteke na disku, dokler se ne izvede operacija shranjevanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applying a Difference"
msgstr "Uporaba razlik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To apply a difference, click the highlighted difference region, then select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Difference</guimenu><guimenuitem>Apply Difference</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo><keycap>Space</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti razliko, kliknite označeno območje razlike in izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Razlika</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uporabi razliko</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo><keycap>Space</keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unapplying a Difference"
msgstr "Neuporaba razlike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To unapply a difference, click the highlighted difference region previously "
"applied, then select <menuchoice><guimenu>Difference</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Unapply Difference</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo>&Backspace;</keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite razveljaviti uporabo razlike, kliknite označeno področje razlike, "
"ki je bilo predhodno uporabljeno, nato izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Razlika</guimenu><guimenuitem>Neuporabi razlike</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo>&Backspace;</keycombo>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applying All Differences"
msgstr "Uporaba vseh razlik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After reviewing differences between files and finding all acceptable it is "
"possible apply them all with a single operation by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Difference</guimenu><guimenuitem>Apply All</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</"
"keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Po pregledu razlik med datotekami in ugotovitvi, da so vse sprejemljive, jih "
"je mogoče uporabiti vse z eno operacijo z izbiro "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Razlike</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uporabi vse</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>A</"
"keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unapplying All Differences"
msgstr "Neuporabi vseh razlik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To revert all differences that have been applied previously select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Difference</guimenu><guimenuitem>Unapply All</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>U</"
"keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite povrniti vse razlike, ki so bile predhodno uporabljene, izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Razlika</guimenu><guimenuitem>Neuporabi vseh</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>U</"
"keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving Changes"
msgstr "Shranjevanje sprememb"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once differences have been applied they can be saved by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> or <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save All</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Ko so razlike uporabljene, jih lahko shranite z izbiro "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani "
"vsel</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applied differences are saved to both the source and destination file."
msgstr "Uporabljene razlike se shranijo v izvorno in ciljno datoteko."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with Diff Files"
msgstr "Delo z diff datotekami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Diff files contain only the changes made between files, or a set of files "
"within a folder system, and may or may not contain a number of context lines "
"before and after line changes. The sum of a line change and its context "
"lines is known a hunk. A diff file therefore may contain multiple hunks from "
"one or more files. When the context lines of two or more hunks overlap, they "
"are considered a single hunk. Diff files can be used to:"
msgstr ""
"Datoteke z razlikami vsebujejo samo spremembe med datotekami ali nizom "
"datotek v sistemu map in lahko vsebujejo ali ne vsebujejo več kontekstnih "
"vrstic pred in za spremembami vrstic. Vsota spremembe črte in njenih "
"kontekstnih črt je znana kot kos. Razlikovalna datoteka lahko zato vsebuje "
"več kosov iz ene ali več datotek. Če se kontekstne črte dveh ali več kosov "
"prekrivajo, se štejejo za en kos. Datoteke z razlikami lahko uporabite za:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Apply the changes contained in the hunks to an original file."
msgstr "Uporabi spremembe, ki jih vsebujejo kosi, na izvirno datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apply the changes contained in the hunks to a file or set of original files "
"within a folder system."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite spremembe, ki jih vsebujejo kosi, v datoteki ali nizu izvirnih "
"datotek v sistemu map."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Modified before being applied to an original file or set of original files "
"within a folder system."
msgstr ""
"Spremenjeno, preden se uporabi za izvirno datoteko ali niz izvirnih datotek "
"v sistemu map."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a Diff"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje diff"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a diff file a comparison must be displayed in &kompare;. Assuming "
"this is the case, then select <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Save Diff...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> This will "
"display the <guilabel>Diff Options</guilabel> dialog (see <xref linkend="
"\"diff-settings\"/> for more information on diff formats and options). After "
"configuring these options, click the <guibutton>Save</guibutton> button and "
"save the diff to a file with the extension <filename class=\"extension\">."
"diff</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti datoteko diff, je treba primerjavo prikazati v oknu "
"&kompare;. Če je tako, potem izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani Diff...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> To bo "
"prikazalo pogovorno okno <guilabel>Možnosti Diff</guilabel> (glejte <xref "
"linkend=\"diff-settings\"/> za več informacij o oblikah in možnostih "
"razlikovanja). Po konfiguriranju teh možnosti kliknite gumb "
"<guibutton>Shrani</guibutton> in shranite razliko v datoteko s končnico "
"<filename class=\"extension\">.diff</filename>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displaying a Diff"
msgstr "Prikaz razlike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to display the contents of a diff file within &kompare; by "
"opening the diff file from <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Open Diff...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Vsebino datoteke diff je mogoče prikazati v programu &kompare; tako da "
"odprete datoteko razlike iz <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Odpri Diff...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When viewing a diff file the hunks between the source and destination file "
"are shown, remember that only the hunks are shown, no unmodified lines will "
"be shown. In some cases a diff file is created with 0 lines of context. In "
"this case only the changed lines will be displayed."
msgstr ""
"Pri pregledovanju datoteke diff so prikazani kosi med izvorno in ciljno "
"datoteko; ne pozabite, da so prikazani samo kosi, nespremenjene vrstice ne "
"bodo prikazane. V nekaterih primerih se ustvari datoteka z 0 vrsticami "
"konteksta. V tem primeru bodo prikazane samo spremenjene vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a diff file contains hunks from multiple files &kompare; displays the "
"hunks from each file one at a time and you can switch between files as "
"though they were real files even though this information is only provided by "
"the diff file contents."
msgstr ""
"Kadar datoteka diff vsebuje kose iz več datotek, &kompare; prikaže kose iz "
"vsake datoteke posebej in med datotekami lahko preklapljate, kot da so prave "
"datoteke, čeprav je ta informacija na voljo le v vsebini datoteke za "
"primerjavo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applying Differences in a Diff File"
msgstr "Uporaba razlik v datoteki diff"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When viewing differences in a diff file it is possible to apply difference "
"as you would when comparing source and destination files (see <xref linkend="
"\"merging-differences\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Pri pregledovanju razlik v datoteki diff je mogoče uporabiti razliko, kot bi "
"jo uporabili pri primerjavi izvorne in ciljne datoteke (glejte <xref linkend="
"\"merging-differences\"/>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "Blending a &URL; with a Diff"
msgstr "Mešanje &URL; z Diff"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In cases where a diff file is provided it is possible to compare the hunks "
"in the diff against a file or folder. To do this select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Blend URL with Diff...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Then input the <guilabel>File/Folder</guilabel> "
"and <guilabel>Diff Output</guilabel> paths."
msgstr ""
"Če je na voljo datoteka diff, je mogoče primerjati kose v razliki z datoteko "
"ali mapo. Za to izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Zmešaj URL z Diff...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Nato "
"vnesite poti <guilabel>Datoteka/Mapa</guilabel> in <guilabel>Diff Izhod</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When viewing differences between a source file and a diff file it is "
"possible to apply difference as you would when comparing source and "
"destination files (see <xref linkend=\"merging-differences\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Pri pregledovanju razlik med izvorno datoteko in datoteko diff je mogoče "
"uporabiti razliko, kot bi jo uporabili pri primerjavi izvorne in ciljne "
"datoteke (glejte <xref linkend=\"merging-differences\"/>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring Preferences"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje nastavitev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kompare; enables users to set appearance preferences for difference "
"formatting in the main interface and set behavioral properties of the diff "
"program. The <guilabel>Preferences</guilabel> dialog can be accessed by "
"selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guisubmenu>Configure "
"&kompare;...</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"&kompare; omogoča uporabnikom, da v glavnem vmesniku nastavijo nastavitve "
"videza za oblikovanje razlik in nastavijo vedenjske lastnosti programa za "
"razlikovanje. Do pogovornega okna <guilabel>Preference</guilabel> lahko "
"dostopate z izbiro <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>konfiguriraj &kompare;...</guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To configure preferences for appearance select the <guilabel>View</guilabel> "
"menu item (see <xref linkend=\"view-settings\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite konfigurirati nastavitve za videz, izberite element menija "
"<guilabel>Pogled</guilabel> (glejte <xref linkend=\"view-settings\"/>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To configure preferences for diff program properties select the "
"<guilabel>Diff</guilabel> menu item (see <xref linkend=\"diff-settings\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite konfigurirati nastavitve za lastnosti programa diff, izberite "
"element menija <guilabel>Diff</guilabel> (glejte <xref linkend=\"diff-"
"settings\"/>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve pogleda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>View</guimenu> page in the <guilabel>Preferences</guilabel> "
"dialog displays the <guilabel>Appearance</guilabel> and <guilabel>Fonts</"
"guilabel> tabbed forms."
msgstr ""
"Na strani <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> v pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Nastavitve</"
"guilabel> sta prikazana obrazca z zavihkoma <guilabel>Videz</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Pisave</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid "Appearance"
msgstr "Videz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Appearance</guilabel> form provides controls to manage the "
"<guilabel>Colors</guilabel> used to denote difference in the main interface, "
"behavior of the <guilabel>Mouse Wheel</guilabel> when jogging up and down "
"and how <guilabel>Tabs to Spaces</guilabel> conversion is managed."
msgstr ""
"Obrazec <guilabel>Videz</guilabel> zagotavlja kontrolnike za upravljanje "
"<guilabel>Barve</guilabel>, ki se uporabljajo za označevanje razlik v "
"glavnem vmesniku, obnašanje <guilabel>Kolesce miške</guilabel> pri teku "
"navzgor in navzdol ter upravljanje pretvorbe <guilabel>Zavihki v prostore</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kompare; Appearance Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kompare; Nastavitve videza</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kompare; Appearance Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kompare; Nastavitve videza</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Group"
msgstr "Skupina barv"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To adjust color preferences used when displaying differences, click the "
"color button to display the <guilabel>Select Color</guilabel> dialog for the "
"following states:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite prilagoditi nastavitve barv, ki se uporabljajo pri prikazovanju "
"razlik, kliknite gumb za barvo, da se prikaže pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Izberite barvo</guilabel> za naslednja stanja:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:435
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removed color"
msgstr "Odstranjena barva"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lines that have been removed, do not exist, between source and destination."
msgstr ""
"Črte, ki so bile odstranjene, med izvorom in ciljnim krajem ne obstajajo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changed color"
msgstr "Spremenjena barva"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lines that have been changed, modified, between source and destination."
msgstr "Vrstice, ki so bile spremenjene, modificirane med virom in ciljem."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid "Added color"
msgstr "Dodana barva"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lines that have been added between source and destination."
msgstr "Vrstice, ki so bile dodane med vir in cilj."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid "Applied color"
msgstr "Uporabljena barva"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any of the above states where the difference has been applied between source "
"and destination."
msgstr ""
"Katera koli od zgornjih stanj, kjer je bila uporabljena razlika med izvorom "
"in namembnim krajem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mouse Wheel"
msgstr "Kolesce miške"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of lines"
msgstr "Število vrstic"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number of lines to jog the differences when turning the mouse wheel "
"forward or backward."
msgstr ""
"Število vrstic za premikanje razlik pri vrtenju kolesca miške naprej ali "
"nazaj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tabs to Spaces"
msgstr "Tabulatorji v presledke"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of spaces to convert a tab character to"
msgstr "Število presledkov za pretvorbo tabulatorskega znaka v"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:462
#, no-c-format
msgid "Convert each tab character to n space characters."
msgstr "Pretvori vsak tabulatorski znak v n presledkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:468
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fonts"
msgstr "Pisave"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kompare; Fonts Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kompare; Nastavitve pisav</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kompare; Fonts Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kompare; Nastavitve pisav</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the font family and size to display when displaying differences."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve pisav Izberite družino in velikost pisave, ki se prikaže pri "
"prikazovanju razlik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:485
#, no-c-format
msgid "Diff Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve Diff"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Diff</guimenu> page in the <guilabel>Preferences</guilabel> "
"dialog displays the <guilabel>Diff</guilabel>, <guilabel>Format</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Options</guilabel> and <guilabel>Exclude</guilabel> tabbed forms. "
"These forms can be used to configure the behavioral properties of the Diff "
"program."
msgstr ""
"Stran <guimenu>Diff</guimenu> v pogovornem oknu <guilabel>Preference</"
"guilabel> prikazuje zavihke <guilabel>Diff</guilabel>, <guilabel>Format</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Možnosti</guilabel> in <guilabel>Izključite</guilabel>. "
"Te obrazce lahko uporabite za konfiguracijo vedenjskih lastnosti programa "
"Diff."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Diff</title>"
msgstr "<title>Diff</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kompare; Diff Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kompare; Diff Nastavitve</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kompare; Diff Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kompare; Diff Nastavitve</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The command used to run the diff program (default <application>diff</"
"application>)."
msgstr ""
"Ukaz za zagon programa diff (privzeto <application>diff</application>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:507
#, no-c-format
msgid "Format"
msgstr "Format"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kompare; Format Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kompare; Nastavitve formata</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kompare; Format Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kompare; Nastavitve formata</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Adjust options for the <guilabel>Output Format</guilabel> and number of "
"<guilabel>Lines of Context</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Prilagodite možnosti za <guilabel>izhodni format</guilabel> in število "
"<guilabel>vrstic konteksta</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:521
#, no-c-format
msgid "Output Format"
msgstr "Izhodni format"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context"
msgstr "Kontekst"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:525
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The context output format adds several lines of context around the lines "
"that differ."
msgstr ""
"Izhodna oblika konteksta doda več vrstic konteksta okoli vrstic, ki se "
"razlikujejo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal"
msgstr "Normalno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The normal output format displays differing lines without any surrounding "
"lines of context."
msgstr ""
"Običajna izhodna oblika prikaže različne vrstice brez okoliških vrstic "
"konteksta."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unified"
msgstr "Združeni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The unified output format is a variation on the context format. It is "
"considered better than context because the output is more compact than that "
"of context as it omits redundant context lines."
msgstr ""
"Združeni izhodni format je različica formata konteksta. Velja za boljšo od "
"konteksta, ker je rezultat bolj kompakten kot pri kontekstu, saj izpusti "
"odvečne vrstice konteksta."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lines of Context"
msgstr "Vrstice konteksta"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:548
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of context lines"
msgstr "Število vrstic konteksta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When performing a diff with context or unified output format use this "
"parameter to control the number of context lines included."
msgstr ""
"Pri izvajanju diff s kontekstom ali združeno izhodno obliko uporabite ta "
"parameter za nadzor števila vključenih vrstic konteksta."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Možnosti"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kompare; Options Settings</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kompare; Nastavitve možnosti</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:565
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kompare; Options Settings</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kompare; Nastavite možnosti</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Options</guilabel> tab form allows configuration of the "
"options supported by the diff program."
msgstr ""
"Obrazec zavihka <guilabel>Moznosti</guilabel> omogoča konfiguracijo "
"možnosti, ki jih podpira program diff."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Splošno"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid "Treat new files as empty"
msgstr "Nove datoteke obravnavajte kot prazne"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With this option enabled diff will treat a file that only exists in one of "
"the directories as empty in the other directory. This means that the file is "
"compared with an empty file and because of this will appear as one big "
"insertion or deletion."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost omogočena, bo diff obravnavalo datoteko, ki obstaja samo v "
"enem od imenikov, kot prazno v drugem imeniku. To pomeni, da se datoteka "
"primerja s prazno datoteko in se zato zdi kot en velik vnos ali brisanje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "Look for smaller changes"
msgstr "Poiščite manjše spremembe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:581
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Forces diff to display changes in case, punctuation, space, &etc; when "
"checked."
msgstr ""
"Prisili diff da prikaže spremembe velikosti črk, ločil, presledkov itd. , ko "
"je to preverjeno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid "Optimize for large files"
msgstr "Optimizacija za velike datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switches diff to process files with high-speed when checked."
msgstr "Preklopi diff na obdelavo datotek z visoko hitrostjo, če je označeno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore changes in case"
msgstr "Ne upoštevajte sprememb v primeru"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:589
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lower and Uppercase character changes are omitted when this option is "
"checked."
msgstr ""
"Spremembe malih in velikih črk so izpuščene, če je ta možnost označena."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore regexp"
msgstr "Ignoriranje regexp"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore lines matching a regular expression."
msgstr "Ignoriranje vrstic, ki ustrezajo regularnemu izrazu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:599
#, no-c-format
msgid "Whitespace"
msgstr "Beli prostor"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand tabs to spaces in output"
msgstr "Razširi tabulatorje na presledke v izpisu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:602
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When checked diff outputs will converts tab characters to the number of "
"spaces defined in the <guilabel>Preferences</guilabel> dialog <guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> menu <guilabel>Tabs to Spaces</guilabel> option."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo diff pretvoril znake tabulatorja v število "
"presledkov, določeno v meniju <guilabel>Preference</guilabel> "
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> menija <guilabel>Zavihki v prostore</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:607
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ignore added or removed empty lines"
msgstr "Ignoriranje dodanih ali odstranjenih praznih vrstic"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"lines of zero length that differ between source and destination are ignored "
"when this option is checked."
msgstr ""
"če je ta možnost označena, se vrstice z ničelno dolžino, ki se razlikujejo "
