#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:829
#, no-c-format
msgid "Commandline Options"
msgstr "Možnosti ukazne vrstice"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:833
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>-c</term>"
msgstr "<term>-c</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:834
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will compare URL1 with URL2."
msgstr "To bo primerjalo URL1 z URL2."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:838
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>kompare</command> <option>-o</option>"
msgstr "<command>kompare</command> <option>-o</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:840
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will open URL1 and expect it to be diff output. URL1 can also be a '-' "
"and then it will read from standard input. Can be used for instance for "
"<userinput><command>cvs diff | kompare -o -</command></userinput>. Kompare "
"will do a check to see if it can find the original file(s) and then blend "
"the original file(s) into the diffoutput and show that in the viewer. "
"<option>-n</option> disables the check."
msgstr ""
"To bo odprlo naslov URL1 in pričakovalo, da bo to razlikovalni izpis. URL1 "
"je lahko tudi '-' in potem se bo bral iz standardnega vhoda. Uporablja se "
"lahko na primer za <userinput><command>cvs diff | kompare -o -</command></"
"userinput>. Kompare bo preveril, ali lahko najde izvirno(-e) datoteko(-e), "
"nato pa izvirno(-e) datoteko(-e) pomešal v izpis razlike in jo prikazal v "
"pregledovalniku. <option>-n</option> onemogoči preverjanje."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:851
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>kompare</command> <option>-b</option>"
msgstr "<command>kompare</command> <option>-b</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:853
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will blend URL2 into URL1, URL2 is expected to be diff output and URL1 "
"the file or folder that the diffoutput needs to be blended into."
msgstr ""
"To bo zmešalo URL2 v URL1, URL2 bo predvidoma izhodni rezultat diff, URL1 pa "
"datoteka ali mapa, v katero je treba zmešati izhodni rezultat."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:860
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>kompare</command> <option>-n</option>"
msgstr "<command>kompare</command> <option>-n</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:862
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Disables the check for automatically finding the original file(s) when using "
"'-' as URL with the <option>-o</option> option."
msgstr ""
"Onemogoči preverjanje samodejnega iskanja izvirnih datotek pri uporabi '-' "
"kot URL z možnostjo <option>-o</option>."

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:868
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kompare</command> <option>-e</option> <replaceable>encoding</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kompare</command> <option>-e</option> <replaceable>encoding</"
"replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:870
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this to specify the encoding when calling it from the command line. It "
"will default to the local encoding if not specified."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite ga za določitev kodiranja, ko ga kličete iz ukazne vrstice. Če ga "
"ne navedete, bo privzeto uporabljeno lokalno kodiranje."

